data-triple-N3.o: "Samuel Dylan Murray Preston (born 16 January 1982), more commonly known as Preston, is an English singer, who is the lead singer of The Ordinary Boys. He also appeared in the reality television show Celebrity Big Brother in 2006, in which he finished fourth. After The Ordinary Boys split in 2008, he embarked on a songwriting career. and is now back leading The Ordinary Boys with a revamped lineup on a December 2011 UK tour."@en
